{"tid":624134,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我只想唱歌俾大家聽","createTime":"2018-04-10T14:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T15:39:27.000Z","uid":132678,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b58605ad767148c306075f0cc3e7b5f3db3b945f","tid":624134,"uid":132678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T14:35:13.000Z","msg":"因為我怕下面介紹自己會講左好多<br />\n所以虛線前係懶人包<br />\n我只係想自己可以COVER一D自己 鍾意既歌 / 覺得好既作品 俾大家聽，<br />\n而自己好多時主要都係唱廣東歌，<br />\n就算幾少都好，希望可以為本土音樂盡一點點綿力。<br />\n希望大家會LIKE我既YOUTUBE CHANNEL / FACEBOOK PAGE，<br />\n希望大家可以多多支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nYOUTUBE CHANNEL：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw&d=bM4oZYWDi3nHJ0eim5ZsHNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=3a6ed5d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw</a><br />\n<br />\nFACEBOOK PAGE：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MOONMANMUSIC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMOONMANMUSIC%2F&d=bM4oZYWDi3nHJ0eim5ZsHNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ca6eb21f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MOONMANMUSIC/</a><br />\n<br />\nEMAIL：<br />\nmoonmanmusic01@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n--------------<br />\n<br />\n在呢到再詳細少少介紹下自己<br />\n小弟其實自小以來主要都係唱歌為興趣<br />\n你問我既夢想，相信香港好多人都係一樣<br />\n當然係想做一個歌手，而且自己一直有學唱歌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而小弟一直以來都有一個小小既理想，<br />\n就係可以開一個平台、有一個地方去SHARE自己 唱/翻唱 既歌俾人，<br />\n其實呢個世代要做呢件事的確唔難，<br />\n但多年以來有好多原因令自己冇咁做到，<br />\n包括自己既能力技巧、器材技術、私人理由等。<br />\n自己亦都唔想好求其咁交到一D野出黎就算。<br />\n<br />\n工作左數年，有時候覺得生活真係好苦悶，<br />\n亦覺得其實都可以嘗試一下俾人聽聽自己一直以來努力既野，<br />\n我唔敢話自己已經唱得有如天皇巨星，<br />\n但最起碼希望做到有人會聽，甚至有人可以見證自己未來既成長。<br />\n<br />\n除左學唱歌，小弟都有接觸唔同既樂器，<br />\n但都只係識少少，亦都有同朋友偶然出下SHOW去唱歌，<br />\n甚至學過下少少編曲作曲，<br />\n但我可以敢講自己現時真完全係冇呢方面既天份同能力，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曾經好想開呢個平台係可以重新編寫、<br />\n用更好既音質既音樂去錄製翻唱再俾大家，<br />\n但可惜結果都係唔成功，而且好失敗。<br />\n曾經亦搵過一D同學/朋友合作，可惜大家都好忙，<br />\n亦都好難好自私咁，要人地義務唔收錢咁去為你做好多野(如編曲、後製等)。<br />\n所以到最後都只能夠用網上一D MMO去錄，<br />\n如果將來有機會，有更好既能力及技術，希望可以帶更好既質素俾大家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實一直以來，身邊好多朋友都叫我，<br />\n＂不過試下放下上網俾人聽啦＂，<br />\n其實自己一直亦都好想咁做，而上面亦都講左有好多原因令自己卻步。<br />\n<br />\n經過一番既準備同思考，總算可以勉強做到少少。<br />\n雖然仲有好多問題，例如網上版權既問題始終唔算好熟識，<br />\n只希望能夠邊做邊學。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而今次其實我係完全冇通知過任何一個朋友，<br />\n甚至冇通知身邊既家人親戚會在呢個時候做呢個平台去俾人聽。<br />\n所以你分分鐘會做左我第一個網上既聽眾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有機會的話會再分享自己更多，<br />\n最後講多句，只要有一個人支持，<br />\n我都會繼續去努力學、繼續去努力做、繼續去努力唱。<br />\n<br />\n如有疑問，可以留言或以各種方式PM我，<br />\n可以回答既我都會盡力回答，多謝。<br />\n希望大家會LIKE我既YOUTUBE CHANNEL / FACEBOOK PAGE，<br />\n希望大家可以多多支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYOUTUBE CHANNEL：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw&d=bM4oZYWDi3nHJ0eim5ZsHNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=3a6ed5d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw</a><br />\n<br />\nFACEBOOK PAGE：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MOONMANMUSIC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMOONMANMUSIC%2F&d=bM4oZYWDi3nHJ0eim5ZsHNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ca6eb21f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MOONMANMUSIC/</a><br />\n<br />\nEMAIL：<br />\nmoonmanmusic01@gmail.com"},{"pid":"f72047961aa43a8f3bf211f0588a0a315583780a","tid":624134,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"2111623f4a2f95a644fc61292e6a7066158b2a3e","tid":624134,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f72047961aa43a8f3bf211f0588a0a315583780a","tid":624134,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T14:38:54.000Z","msg":"hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9d2bb2b2ce37b17126d9a265eee449cdfde310","tid":624134,"uid":132678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2111623f4a2f95a644fc61292e6a7066158b2a3e","tid":624134,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f72047961aa43a8f3bf211f0588a0a315583780a","tid":624134,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T14:38:54.000Z","msg":"hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f142c7ab54b072808aa0591bf5c0c55f2b8a171","tid":624134,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"ok ar <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},{"pid":"7cd80fdd2a4a3e04dcb1bf5b5d8c97afd47db86a","tid":624134,"uid":132678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f142c7ab54b072808aa0591bf5c0c55f2b8a171","tid":624134,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"ok ar <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人支持好感動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94445408edbb8e8289